{"tid":410534,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"FIFA最佳入球最後十強: 豬腦蠍子擺尾！","createTime":"2017-09-23T04:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-28T10:36:52.000Z","uid":31314,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b6425405cc1dc92fd7ef4b33f9706e9a61d5334","tid":410534,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:33:16.000Z","msg":"國際足協公佈了2017年度最佳入球暨普斯卡斯獎的10大候選入球，基奧特、文素基治和馬迪的精彩入球均名列其中。10月9日，普斯卡斯獎將在其中選出三個入球進入最後的角逐，最終會花落誰家呢？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>1.M子，祖記VS皇馬，歐冠盃，2017年6月3日</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n希古恩胸部停球後將球一墊做給M子，後者胸部停球後直接淩空倒掛射門，幫助球隊扳平了比數。雖然最終祖記輸掉了比賽，但是M子的這粒入球將永遠與這次決賽一同被球迷們銘記。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jFpiRefXX04&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjFpiRefXX04%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=QHPTG5eaz2GpMCGqPCcVe9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=d3e51612\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jFpiRefXX04&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2.豬蛇，阿仙奴VS水晶宮，英超，2017年1月1日</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n豬蛇2017年的新年第一球來的十分特別，在與水晶宮隊的比賽中，山齊士左路傳中，中路跟進的基奧特面對稍稍靠後的皮球選擇用一腳蠍子擺尾式的鉤射完成破門。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jFpiRefXX04&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjFpiRefXX04%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=QHPTG5eaz2GpMCGqPCcVe9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=d3e51612\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jFpiRefXX04&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>3.馬迪，車路士VS熱刺，足總盃，2017年4月22日</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n2017年英格蘭足總盃4強，車路士對陣熱刺，後備上場的馬迪在一次插上進攻中接隊友分球直接張弓搭箭爆射球門死角，幫助球隊將比數鎖定在了4-2。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XC32CprP10Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXC32CprP10Y&d=QHPTG5eaz2GpMCGqPCcVe9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=7f5f3e5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XC32CprP10Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>4.奇雲-保定，維拉利爾VS拉斯彭馬斯，西甲，2016年10月23日</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/M7YdC1-VQ2c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FM7YdC1-VQ2c&d=QHPTG5eaz2GpMCGqPCcVe9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=d8eacb4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/M7YdC1-VQ2c</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>5.穆沙-迪比利，聖約翰斯通VS些路迪，蘇超，2017年2月5</strong></span>日<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/r3gElnGrQes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fr3gElnGrQes&d=QHPTG5eaz2GpMCGqPCcVe9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=c8706026\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/r3gElnGrQes</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>6.卡馬爾格，康塞普西翁大學VS奧希堅斯，智利超級聯賽，2016年12月4日</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Czgau5tQwZI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCzgau5tQwZI&d=QHPTG5eaz2GpMCGqPCcVe9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=62687600\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Czgau5tQwZI</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>7.卡斯特利亞諾斯，委內瑞拉VS喀麥隆，U17女足世界盃，2016年10月3日</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ryX4qy7PrPc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FryX4qy7PrPc&d=QHPTG5eaz2GpMCGqPCcVe9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=3092a91d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ryX4qy7PrPc</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>8.胡爾塔多，阿特拉斯VS蒂華納，墨西哥甲級聯賽，2017年4月1日</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GlvbLjhWU1I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGlvbLjhWU1I&d=QHPTG5eaz2GpMCGqPCcVe9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=46840f75\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GlvbLjhWU1I</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>9.馬蘇盧基，巴洛卡VS奧蘭多海盜，南非超級聯賽，2016年11月30日</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Z0FHfkAHmyE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZ0FHfkAHmyE&d=QHPTG5eaz2GpMCGqPCcVe9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=9a526d05\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Z0FHfkAHmyE</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>10.姆布拉，巴塞VS多蒙特，青年歐冠盃，2017年2月22日</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Qu_XKyYcqIQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQu_XKyYcqIQ&d=QHPTG5eaz2GpMCGqPCcVe9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=0c7fffc0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Qu_XKyYcqIQ</a>"},{"pid":"ec24bc699eaaac49ecb277a0a6d7535072a83c71","tid":410534,"uid":70013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:37:09.000Z","msg":"1,2同一條link"},{"pid":"04431596ad71a38a0cc4cf23b5ee8a0c5f29a76a","tid":410534,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:40:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1,2同一條link</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wGOhxt5Ksc0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwGOhxt5Ksc0&d=QHPTG5eaz2GpMCGqPCcVe9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=2eb12112\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wGOhxt5Ksc0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c71976a17bd63d68e88b52e783402bc1f1e2c933","tid":410534,"uid":10338,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:42:11.000Z","msg":"奇雲保定果球好似睇緊少林足球"},{"pid":"faca8791c9020194280de8e299c4ecfef99aea41","tid":410534,"uid":22989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:42:24.000Z","msg":"十卜M子"},{"pid":"f38095abf75033ed2fa03db09af9f784b5442ad6","tid":410534,"uid":10576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:49:18.000Z","msg":"龍門入倒掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f7becb3cfe48b7f2aa5b52f6851e89dacc3e9c","tid":410534,"uid":3363,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":